I'm trying to
stay grounded.

23:03.925 --> 23:05.836
Good to have you back.

23:07.554 --> 23:09.840
How'd you get this?
The issue isn't even out yet.

23:09.931 --> 23:12.718
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

23:14.143 --> 23:18.728
