l freeze time, too.

23:25.780 --> 23:28.146
Stop the explosion.
Saved your dad.

23:29.492 --> 23:31.733
Hey, didn't you visit my mom?

23:31.828 --> 23:32.863
Hmm?

23:32.954 --> 23:35.240
We should get them
