I called the police.

23:38.793 --> 23:40.579
Time to go, Micah.

23:40.670 --> 23:43.127
Dad, you saved her
like a real hero.

23:43.214 --> 23:45.375
Now we can go back
and save Morn.

23:45.466 --> 23:47.377
