We just go back.

23:50.054 --> 23:53.217
No, Micah, it's not.

23:54.684 --> 23:57.016
I'm sorry.
We can't go back.

23:58.313 --> 24:00.019
We can never go back.

24:04.027 --> 24:05.517
Come on.

24:15.246 --> 24:16.452
Bye-bye.

24:16.539 --> 24:17.870
Take care.

24:18.458 --> 24:20.494
(POLICE SIREN WAILING)

24:28.593 --> 24:31.209
Come on!
You can't stay
in there forever!

24:33.973 --> 24:35.929
Would you just
give me the damn tape?

24:36.017 --> 24:39.054
I'm gonna put
this thing on YouTube,
make like a million bucks.

24:39.145 --> 24:40.646
YouTube is free, you idiot.

24:40.730 --> 24:42.470
You're not helping.

24:43.691 --> 24:46.182
Lyle, no one can see
what's on that tape.

24:46.277 --> 24:47.813
Are you
an alien or something?

24:47.904 --> 24:49.269
Is he an alien, too?

24:49.364 --> 24:51.946
Yeah, yeah,
we're gonna anal probe you.

24:52.492 --> 24:54.733
Zach, stop scaring him.

24:55.244 --> 24:57.496
I'm not coming out
until Mom and Dad get home.

24:57.580 --> 25:00.572
No. No, no, no, no.
You cannot tell them.

25:01.584 --> 25:05.247
Lyle, please,
they cannot find out
about this.

25:05.463 --> 25:06.498
Why not?

25:06.589 --> 25:07.829
Don't you get it?

25:07.924 --> 25:10.540
If they found out,
Mom and Dad would

25:11.094 --> 25:13.801
think it was
a mistake to ever adopt me.

25:16.140 --> 25:18.176
We wouldn't be
a family anymore.

25:26.109 --> 25:27.440
Please.

25:37.495 --> 25:38.530
Thank you.

25:38.621 --> 25:39.827
Whatever.

25:46.170 --> 25:47.455
(YELLS)

25:49.757 --> 25:51.918
Wait a minute,
wait a second.

25:52.009 --> 25:54.170
We're going in here
without backup?

25:54.262 --> 25:56.344
No on even knows
we're here, do they?

25:56.431 --> 25:58.797
What is this
all about with you?

25:58.891 --> 26:01.052
