all burned off.

26:57.825 --> 26:59.361
(THUDDING)

27:27.313 --> 27:29.395
(GEIGER COUNTER
CLICKING RAPIDLY)

27:29.982 --> 27:32.598
What the hell
happened in here?

27:33.236 --> 27:35.773
Eighteen hundred
curies of radiation.

27:35.863 --> 27:38.195
Come on,
let's get out of here.

27:43.746 --> 27:46.078
Of course I'm gonna
vote for Nathan. Yep.

27:46.707 --> 27:48.698
lf Nathan takes
care of the people

27:48.793 --> 27:51.751
half as much as
he takes care of his brother,

27:51.838 --> 27:53.749
it's gonna be
an interesting city.

27:53.840 --> 27:55.671
Pretty special family.

27:55.758 --> 27:57.259
You have no idea.

27:58.928 --> 28:01.840
DENNISON: This is all
very inspiring.

28:01.931 --> 28:05.515
l was surprised to learn
the Linderman group recently
invested in your campaign.

28:05.601 --> 28:06.807
I don't know
why you'd be surprised.

28:06.894 --> 28:08.350
Mr. Linderman was
a good friend of my father's.

28:08.437 --> 28:12.601
So, you don't deny going
to Las Vegas to meet
with a reputed mobster?

28:15.862 --> 28:16.897
Is that why you're here?

28:16.988 --> 28:19.024
I spoke with a former member
of your security detail.

28:19.115 --> 28:21.276
It seems there was
a bit of a scare,

28:22.285 --> 28:25.777
that you disappeared
from the casino
for several hours,

28:26.747 --> 28:28.908
and there was
a blond involved.

28:35.798 --> 28:39.632
It's all right, Nathan.
You can tell him.

28:41.971 --> 28:43.677
Right...

28:44.640 --> 28:49.304
I'm sure you've
recently heard about
my mental health issues.

28:51.314 --> 28:53.555
I quit my job because of it.

28:53.649 --> 28:57.016
My brother
basically saved my life,

28:57.445 --> 29:00.528
and he's convinced me
to get the help
that I needed.

29:00.615 --> 29:04.984
There's a private
clinic outside Vegas.

29:05.912 --> 29:09.575
Nathan went,
spoke to a doctor,
a woman doctor.

29:10.666 --> 29:13.453
I made him promise
that no one would know.

29:13.753 --> 29:19.623
Not even the family,
but I just don't care
who knows anymore.

29:20.676 --> 29:22.177
Okay?

29:22.762 --> 29:26.346
I didn't want to say
anything until
l'd cleared it with you.

29:27.683 --> 29:30.425
That's Nathan. You know,
right in the middle
of an election

29:30.519 --> 29:34.011
he still has time to help out
his messed up little brother.

29:34.357 --> 29:35.517
Oh, well...

29:40.571 --> 29:42.687
What's this?
They counteract
the radiation poisoning.

29:42.782 --> 29:44.113
Oh, thanks.

29:44.200 --> 29:45.485
