29:54.168 --> 29:55.408
Since when is
your wife nobody?

29:55.503 --> 29:57.585
Listen, I don't think
this guy's Sylar.

29:57.672 --> 30:00.379
Yeah? Well, we'll see.

30:00.466 --> 30:03.458
Look what I found in bedroom.
Look at this. Methotrexate.

30:03.552 --> 30:05.634
This is chemotherapy
in a pill.

30:05.721 --> 30:08.713
This is prescribed
to Karen Sprague
and it's current.

30:09.350 --> 30:10.339
She has cancer?

30:10.434 --> 30:12.470
Check out
the doctor on the label.

30:12.561 --> 30:14.097
Dr. Robert Fresco.
Right.

30:14.188 --> 30:15.803
The oncologist.
Mmm-hmm.

30:15.898 --> 30:17.729
Karen Sprague's room?

30:18.067 --> 30:20.228
(WOMAN CHATTER/NG ON PA)

30:25.241 --> 30:27.357
(ECG BEEPING)

30:28.744 --> 30:32.236
Take it easy, Ted.
We just want to
ask you some questions.

30:32.623 --> 30:34.329
I didn't mean to kill him.

30:34.417 --> 30:37.750
Dr. Fresco said
there was nothing
he could do to save her.

30:37.837 --> 30:39.327
I tried to convince him,
you know.

30:39.422 --> 30:42.334
There must be
something else
that he could do.

30:42.425 --> 30:43.631
Anything.

30:44.677 --> 30:48.340
